Distribution. A relatively rare species tending to inhabit tropical waters. Recorded from the Mediterranean Sea, off Messina and Sicily; the northern Atlantic ( 20–35 °N), and the North Pacific Ocean, in the east from central California to the equator, and in the west from the China Sea region. There is also one record from the central southern Indian Ocean ( 41 °S 58 °E;
Vinogradov & Semenova 1996
). The above record from the Tasman Sea is the first for this region.
